org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.model.tree
Class DynNode<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.model.tree.DynNode<T>
Type Parameters:
T - 
public final class DynNode<T>
extends java.lang.Object

DynNode represent a node in the red-black interval tree IntervalTree. To each node is associated an interval DynInterval and a color (black or red).

Author:
Sabina Sara Pfister
